# Tailwind CSS Rules

## Tailwind setup (v4 / QuizMaker)

- This app uses **Tailwind CSS v4** with **`@tailwindcss/postcss`** (see **`quizmaker-app/postcss.config.mjs`**). Global entry is **`src/app/globals.css`** (e.g. **`@import "tailwindcss"`** and shadcn-related imports). There may be **no** root **`tailwind.config.ts`**—follow existing **`globals.css`** and **`quizmaker-app/components.json`** for paths and theme tokens when adding or extending UI.

## Styling

- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes directly on components.
- Do not write custom CSS unless absolutely necessary.
- Follow the component styling guidelines for consistency.
